Package: hpiR
Type: Package
Title: House Price Indexes in R
Version: 0.2.0
Author: c(person('Andy', 'Krause', role=c('aut', 'cre'), 
    email=akrause@greenfieladadvisors.com))
Maintainer: Andy Krause <andy@greenfieldadvisors.com>
Description: Compute house price indexes using a variety of different methods and
    models common through the real estate literature.  Evaluate index 'goodness' based
    on accuracy, volatility and revision statistics.
